snippet.title: Mario Party Star Rush - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Discover instant fun for everyone in Mario Party Star Rush. Packed with fast, fun modes and mini-games this party offers something for everyone! It’s always your turn as you and up to three* friends roll the dice, roam the board, and recruit fan-favorite allies. (*Additional games and systems required for multiplayer mode. Sold Separately.) Mario Party Star Rush for Nintendo 3DS. Available Now! #MarioParty

Check Out Mario Party Star Rush! http://marioparty.nintendo.com
